---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label reveal"><span class="idx">01 /</span> About</div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">A builder who thinks in models.</h2>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
          I'm an AI/ML engineer studying Computer Science and Operations Research at Cornell. I like taking messy data and black-box models and making them observable, testable, and reliable enough to trust in production.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
          Beyond that, I'm drawn to the frontier of the field — LLMs, agentic systems, reinforcement learning, and the research pushing all three forward.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-4">
          When I'm not coding, you'll find me out running on a trail, in the gym, or halfway through the latest YouTube video essay that wandered into my feed.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-sheet reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="spec-key">Location</span>
          <span class="spec-value">Wayne, PA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="spec-key">Education</span>
          <span class="spec-value">B.S. Computer Science &amp; Operations Research — Cornell University</span>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="spec-key">Focus</span>
          <span class="spec-value">Classical ML · Modern AI / LLMs · Full-stack systems</span>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="spec-key">Toolkit</span>
          <span class="spec-value">Python · PyTorch · TypeScript · FastAPI</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
